OL,5,G1715 FIFA WC2026: Canada v Morocco
OL,6,     FCanada v Morocco (Kick-off
OL,7,     F6.00pm). Coverage of the first
OL,8,     Fround-of-16 match, which takes
OL,9,     Fplace at Houston Stadium in the
OL,10,     FUSA. Canada edged past South
OL,11,     FAfrica 1-0 in the last round, in a
OL,12,     Fmatch that is unlikely to live
OL,13,     Flong in the memory, but the
OL,14,     FCanadians won't let that bother
OL,15,     Fthem, although they'll be
OL,16,     Funderdogs this time against a side
OL,17,     Flooking to emulate their
OL,18,     Fachievements of four years ago,
OL,19,     Fwhen they reached the semi-finals.
OL,20,     FMorocco come into this match on
